# Telos Endless Dogfood Research Program

Date started: 2026-07-01

Purpose: run pass after pass across markets, sciences, mathematics, compute, and societal domains using Project Telos tooling as the research substrate.

This folder is the durable ledger for ongoing dogfood research. Each pass should add:

- a pass ledger entry;
- one or more domain packets;
- source receipts or source URLs;
- a falsifiable thesis;
- an adversarial/steelman section;
- a tool-use receipt summary;
- a next-pass queue.

Ground rule: no packet may claim a new natural law, solved theorem, biological result, material discovery, or societal conclusion unless the evidence packet actually proves it. Early passes may produce hypotheses, identities, negative results, proof attempts, reproducible numerical probes, and internal system laws.

