| `PROBE_MATCH` | A bounded computation matched the expected behavior. |
| `CRUCIBLE_MATCH` | Crucible assessed a claim as matching the measurement packet. |
| `UNVERIFIABLE` | Evidence is insufficient or inaccessible. |
